Another insightful geometric example is given by the relative homology of formula_102 where formula_103. Then we can use the long exact sequence
:formula_104
Using exactness of the sequence we can see that formula_105 contains a loop formula_106 counterclockwise around the origin. Since the cokernel of formula_107 fits into the exact sequence
:formula_108
it must be isomorphic to formula_109. One generator for the cokernel is the formula_110-chain formula_111 since its boundary map is
:formula_112

